Live migration:
Used when Host system needs to be updated(Hardware or software update) when the Vm instances are running.
Not supported for preemptible vms

On Host Maintanance:
->Migrate i.e., Migrate Vm to another host if current host is updated
->Terminate i.e Stop the instance in case of Host updation


Automatic restart:(On/Off)
Compute Engine can automatically restart VM instances
if they are terminated for non-user-initiated reasons (maintenance event, hardware failure, software failure and so on)

